GTE Corp filed with the Securitiesand Exchange Commission for a shelf offering of four mln sharesof auction preferred stock on terms to be set at the time ofsale.    The dividend rate on the shares is reset by auction every49 days. The shares will be offered in units of 1,000 and eachunit will have a liquidation preference of 100,000 dlrs. Anunderwriting group will be led by Goldman, Sachs and Co.    GTE said proceeds will be used to reduce short-term debtand to partially fund repurchases of common stock. Reuter&#3;